* <a href="http://practicingruby.com/articles/shared/vbmlgkdtahzd">Issue 2.6: Learning new things step-by-step</a>
* <a href="http://practicingruby.com/articles/shared/ozkzbsdmagcm">Issue 2.7: "Unobtrusive Ruby" in Practice</a>
* <a href="http://practicingruby.com/articles/shared/jleygxejeopq">Issue 2.8: Ruby and the singleton pattern don't get along</a>
* <a href="http://practicingruby.com/articles/shared/qyxvmrgmhuln">Issue 2.9: Building Unix-style command line applications</a>
